content:
Milestones on support records display one of three statuses:

Compliant - Milestones are complete or not in violation.
Open Violation - One or more milestones have been violated, and steps are incomplete.
Closed Violation - One or more milestones were violated, but steps were still completed.

The status icons differ based on where the milestone appears and whether you're in Salesforce Classic or Lightning Experience.

In Salesforce Classic:
On the Milestone Status Icon field and Case Milestones related list
